import React, { createContext, useReducer } from 'react';


const initialState = {
    nav: {
        bg: '#D9E9F4',
        logoContainer: '#A3C7D4',
        h1: '#8DAFB7',
        hamburger: '#C2D8E2',
        hamDiv: '#E4F1FB',

        cart: '#A3C7D4',
    },
    landing: {
        bg: '#D9E9F4',

    offeringSchema: {
        bg: 'rgba(217, 233, 244, 0.9)',
        bgHover: 'rgba(217, 233, 244, 1)',
        icon: '#A3C7D4',
        iconHover: '#C2D8E2',
        title: '#8DAFB7',
        description: '#6A8F99',
        styledLink: '#C2D8E2',
        styledLinkHover: '#A3C7D4',
    },
    offering: {
        bg: 'rgba(217, 233, 244, 0.8)',
        introduction: 'rgba(217, 233, 244, 0.7)',
        introH1: '#8DAFB7',
        introH2: '#A3C7D4',
        introP: '#5A7D8C',
        offers: 'rgba(201, 227, 249, 0.03)',
    },
    contact: {
        bg: '#D9E9F4',
        title: '#8DAFB7',
        description: '#6A8F99',
        socialLinks: '#C2D8E2',
        socialLink: '#A3C7D4',
    },
    clientCounter: {
        bg: 'rgba(217, 233, 244, 0.9)',
        countWrapper: 'rgba(217, 233, 244, 0.8)',
        number: '#A3C7D4',
        counter: '#C2D8E2',
    },
    about: {
        bg: '#D9E9F4',
        aboutSection: '#E4F1FB',
        aboutSectionH1: '#8DAFB7',
        aboutSectionH2: '#A3C7D4',
        aboutSectionP: '#5A7D8C',
        faq: '#C2D8E2',
        dropdown: '#A3C7D4',
        dropdownH1: '#8DAFB7',
        answer: '#E4F1FB',
        answerP: '#6A8F99',
    },
    footer: {
        bg: '#D9E9F4',
        footWrapper: '#D9E9F4',
        section: '#8DAFB7',
        companyTitile: '#A3C7D4',
        companyDescription: '#5A7D8C',
        sectionTitile: '#6A8F99',
        styledLink: '#C2D8E2',
        finalSection: '#E4F1FB',
        finalText: '#8DAFB7',
        finalLink: '#A3C7D4',
    },
    register: {
        bg: '#E4F1FB',
        left: '#FFFFFF',
        bigCircleGradient: 'rgba(179, 212, 252, 0.4)',
        bigCircleGradient2: 'rgba(144, 202, 249, 0.2)',
        c1: '#B3D4FC',
        c2: '#90CAF9',
        c3: '#42A5F5',
        c4: '#1E88E5',
        welcome: '#1565C0',
        description: '#1A237E',
        linktext: '#0D47A1',
        styledLink: '#1976D2',
        right: '#E3F2FD',
        container: '#FFFFFF',
        heading: '#0D47A1',
        input: '#BBDEFB',
        inputBorder: '#90CAF9',
        inputTextColor: '#1E88E5',
        inputShadow: '0 2px 4px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.2)',
        inputBorderHover: '#1E88E5',
        inputHover: '#E3F2FD',
        inputShadowHover: '0 4px 6px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.2)',
        inputFocus: '#0D47A1',
        registerBtn: '#1976D2',
        registerBtnHover: '#1565C0',
        registerBtnShadow: '#42A5F5',
        registerBtnShadowHover: '#1565C0',
        responseMsg: '#388E3C',
    },
    
    login: {
        bg: '#E4F1FB',
        left: '#FFFFFF',
        bigCircleGradient: 'rgba(179, 212, 252, 0.4)',
        bigCircleGradient2: 'rgba(144, 202, 249, 0.2)',
        c1: '#B3D4FC',
        c2: '#90CAF9',
        c3: '#42A5F5',
        c4: '#1E88E5',
        welcome: '#1565C0',
        description: '#1A237E',
        linktext: '#0D47A1',
        styledLink: '#1976D2',
        right: '#E3F2FD',
        container: '#FFFFFF',
        heading: '#0D47A1',
        input: '#BBDEFB',
        inputBorder: '#90CAF9',
        inputTextColor: '#1E88E5',
        inputShadow: '0 2px 4px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.2)',
        inputBorderHover: '#1E88E5',
        inputHover: '#E3F2FD',
        inputShadowHover: '0 4px 6px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.2)',
        inputFocus: '#0D47A1',
        registerBtn: '#1976D2',
        registerBtnHover: '#1565C0',
        registerBtnShadow: '#42A5F5',
        registerBtnShadowHover: '#1565C0',
        responseMsg: '#388E3C',
    },
};


const reducer = (state, action) => {
    switch (action.type) {

        default:
            return state
    }
}

export const colorContext = createContext();
const ColorContextProvider = ({ children }) => {

    const [config, dispatchConfig] = useReducer(reducer, initialState)

    return (
        <colorContext.Provider value={{ config, dispatchConfig }}>
            {children}
        </colorContext.Provider>
    );
};

export default ColorContextProvider;
